code: @Test public void defaultHealthIndicatorNameFactory() {     ReactiveHealthIndicatorRegistry registry = this.factory.createReactiveHealthIndicatorRegistry(Collections.singletonMap("myHealthIndicator", () -> Mono.just(UP)), null).     assertThat(registry.getAll()).containsOnlyKeys("my"). }

@Test public void healthIndicatorIsAdapted() {     ReactiveHealthIndicatorRegistry registry = this.factory.createReactiveHealthIndicatorRegistry(Collections.singletonMap("test", () -> Mono.just(UP)), Collections.singletonMap("regular", () -> DOWN)).     assertThat(registry.getAll()).containsOnlyKeys("test", "regular").     StepVerifier.create(registry.get("regular").health()).consumeNextWith((h) -> {         assertThat(h.getStatus()).isEqualTo(Status.DOWN).         assertThat(h.getDetails()).isEmpty().     }).verifyComplete(). }
